00:54:45,980 --> 00:54:46,940
 idem ja to provjeriti.

955
00:54:46,940 --> 00:54:48,040
 Ona kaže, ovo je super,

956
00:54:48,040 --> 00:54:49,720
 pokušaj ovo izdat.

957
00:54:49,720 --> 00:54:51,960
 I hodem, nađem izdavašku u kuću.

958
00:54:51,960 --> 00:54:54,920
 Sve pođe, malo, pomalo plaća što mogu

959
00:54:54,920 --> 00:54:56,820
 i jako mi je teško da sam dobila otkaza.

960
00:54:56,820 --> 00:54:58,460
 To sve je jako, jako skupo.

961
00:54:58,460 --> 00:55:00,180
 Ja sam mislila, nema ništa od tog.

962
00:55:00,800 --> 00:55:03,220
 Bukvalno zadnji dan me zovila neko ko firma rekla,

963
00:55:03,220 --> 00:55:04,000
 mi ćemo ti pomoć,

964
00:55:04,000 --> 00:55:05,200
 ali smo da izdaješ u koncu.

965
00:55:05,200 --> 00:55:08,300
 Mislim, ljudi nisu bili zainteresiran jer je ljeto bilo,

966
00:55:08,300 --> 00:55:09,820
 ja izdajem u noslikovnicu,

967
00:55:09,820 --> 00:55:12,120
 koja se zove pravi smisao Božića,

968
00:55:12,120 --> 00:55:14,080
 ono, pre rano im je bilo.

969
00:55:14,080 --> 00:55:16,600
 I tako nekako, malo, pomalo,

970
00:55:16,600 --> 00:55:19,000
 nađem tiskaru sve.

971
00:55:19,000 --> 00:55:21,000
 I danas sam najzahvalnija,

972
00:55:21,000 --> 00:55:23,480
 Boga, što se sve to izdogađalo

973
00:55:23,480 --> 00:55:24,280
 i preko ljeta,

974
00:55:24,280 --> 00:55:25,700
 i što sam ostalo bez posla,

975
00:55:25,700 --> 00:55:28,040
 i što sam dobila da radim sa velikom,

976
00:55:28,080 --> 00:55:29,020
 i sa malom djecom,

977
00:55:29,020 --> 00:55:31,260
 i što je nekako sve to imalo svoj put.

978
00:55:31,260 --> 00:55:33,020
 Prekrasno.

979
00:55:33,020 --> 00:55:35,840
 Tu imamo jedan primjerak knjige

980
00:55:35,840 --> 00:55:37,320
 Pravi smisao Božića.

981
00:55:37,320 --> 00:55:39,920
 Nisem mi rekao kako si došla do teme Božića,

982
00:55:39,920 --> 00:55:43,060
 spominjala si svoju djecu i rad s njima,

983
00:55:43,060 --> 00:55:46,120
 i to kako ste vi prolazili,

984
00:55:46,120 --> 00:55:47,080
 što je došašće,

985
00:55:47,080 --> 00:55:48,120
 i koliko ti je važno bilo

986
00:55:48,120 --> 00:55:49,680
 da djeca znaju što je Božić.

987
00:55:50,360 --> 00:55:52,100
 nacrtala,

988
00:55:52,100 --> 00:55:53,700
 prošli Božić,

989
00:55:53,700 --> 00:55:55,860
 kako se on je ono prilično mali,

990
00:55:55,860 --> 00:55:56,440
 kod nas djeca,

991
00:55:56,440 --> 00:55:58,780
 stvarno ne znam kako je u Hrvatskoj,

992
00:55:58,780 --> 00:56:00,540
 ali kod nas djeca već sa šest godina,

993
00:56:00,540 --> 00:56:02,120
 ono, kreću u školu,

994
00:56:02,120 --> 00:56:03,600
 čak i ranije neka.

995
00:56:03,600 --> 00:56:05,720
 Ja dala sam im papirče,

996
00:56:05,720 --> 00:56:06,400
 one male bjela,

997
00:56:06,400 --> 00:56:06,740
 je rekla,

998
00:56:06,740 --> 00:56:08,160
 kad vam kažem riječ Božić,

999
00:56:08,160 --> 00:56:09,360
 ono,

1000
00:56:09,360 --> 00:56:11,020
 ono što vas socira Božić,

1001
00:56:11,020 --> 00:56:11,880
 nacrtajte.

1002
00:56:12,740 --> 00:56:14,260
 i većinom je se

1003
00:56:14,260 --> 00:56:16,520
 jedan poznati sok gaziran,

1004
00:56:16,520 --> 00:56:17,880
 ja da ne spominjemo,

1005
00:56:17,880 --> 00:56:19,440
 svi su to ocrtali,

1006
00:56:19,440 --> 00:56:20,820
 znači više nije ni,

1007
00:56:20,820 --> 00:56:22,860
 više nije ni ono,

1008
00:56:22,860 --> 00:56:23,540
 djed Božić,

1009
00:56:23,540 --> 00:56:24,740
 više nije ni bor,

1010
00:56:24,740 --> 00:56:25,580
 glavni smisal,

1011
00:56:25,580 --> 00:56:26,280
 ni sarma,

1012
00:56:26,280 --> 00:56:28,040
 sad je sok,

1013
00:56:28,040 --> 00:56:29,200
 ja ono,

1014
00:56:29,200 --> 00:56:30,460
 Bože moj dragi,

1015
00:56:30,460 --> 00:56:31,900
 i napišem im basnu,

1016
00:56:31,900 --> 00:56:33,460
 o tom što je zapravo

1017
00:56:33,460 --> 00:56:34,640
 smisao Božića,

1018
00:56:34,640 --> 00:56:36,840
 ali moje sve basne

1019
00:56:36,840 --> 00:56:38,260
 koje pišem i pjesme i sve,

1020
00:56:38,260 --> 00:56:39,620
 da čovjek stane i razmisli

1021
00:56:39,620 --> 00:56:41,020
 koja je poluka priče,

1022
00:56:41,020 --> 00:56:41,820
 nema kraja,

1023
00:56:42,220 --> 00:56:43,820
 nego ti trebaš doći

1024
00:56:43,820 --> 00:56:46,380
 do smisla toga,

1025
00:56:46,380 --> 00:56:48,440
 i ništa,

1026
00:56:48,440 --> 00:56:49,600
 to sam ja samo njima napisala,

1027
00:56:49,600 --> 00:56:50,240
 objavljena strana,

1028
00:56:50,240 --> 00:56:51,420
 su nije par ljudi vidjela,

1029
00:56:51,420 --> 00:56:52,640
 nikog nije zanimalo to,

1030
00:56:52,640 --> 00:56:54,420
 ali mu se učiteljica par javljava,

1031
00:56:54,420 --> 00:56:55,280
 može šli okon tom,

1032
00:56:55,280 --> 00:56:55,480
 ono,

1033
00:56:55,480 --> 00:56:56,600
 prije dobro priča,

1034
00:56:56,600 --> 00:56:57,620
 zašto ljudi ne čitaju,

1035
00:56:57,620 --> 00:56:58,540
 zašto nije toliko,

1036
00:56:58,540 --> 00:56:58,860
 ono,

1037
00:56:58,860 --> 00:57:00,980
 i ostavim je tako sa strane,

1038
00:57:00,980 --> 00:57:02,740
 i ove godine sam misla

1039
00:57:02,740 --> 00:57:04,940
 izdat skroz drugu basnu,

1040
00:57:04,940 --> 00:57:05,840
 ali me ta basna,

1041
00:57:05,840 --> 00:57:07,220
 imam drugu pričku,

1042
00:57:07,220 --> 00:57:07,940
 a je sigurno,

1043
00:57:07,940 --> 00:57:09,700
 marketinjski puno bolja,

1044
00:57:09,920 --> 00:57:11,900
 koju bi ljudi više kupovali,

1045
00:57:11,900 --> 00:57:12,520
 voljeli,

1046
00:57:12,520 --> 00:57:14,640
 i bolje ilustrirana,

1047
00:57:14,640 --> 00:57:16,560
 a samogodu ušla je rovo fali

1048
00:57:16,560 --> 00:57:17,400
 našoj djeci.

1049
00:57:18,200 --> 00:57:19,820
 trenerca Petra iz Mostara,

1050
00:57:19,820 --> 00:57:21,400
 koja surađuje s nama,

1051
00:57:21,400 --> 00:57:22,860
 kad je djeci,

1052
00:57:22,860 --> 00:57:24,560
 on će otvoriti promociju,

1053
00:57:24,560 --> 00:57:25,520
 koja će biti u Mostaru,

1054
00:57:25,520 --> 00:57:26,760
 kad je djeci objašnjavala

1055
00:57:26,760 --> 00:57:27,500
 o čemu se radi,

1056
00:57:27,500 --> 00:57:29,120
 no, pa šta je Božić?

1057
00:57:29,120 --> 00:57:31,040
 Dok je ona došla do riječi Isus,

1058
00:57:31,040 --> 00:57:32,640
 treba joj cijeli trening,

1059
00:57:32,640 --> 00:57:33,540
 da neko spomene,

1060
00:57:33,540 --> 00:57:35,280
 da je Isus vezan s Božićem.

1061
00:57:35,280 --> 00:57:36,700
 No, zove me naskira,

1062
00:57:36,700 --> 00:57:37,280
 na sve gori,

1063
00:57:37,280 --> 00:57:38,300
 molim te,

1064
00:57:38,300 --> 00:57:40,300
 roditeljima treba pričat,

1065
00:57:40,300 --> 00:57:41,000
 ne djeci,

1066
00:57:41,000 --> 00:57:41,860
 jer ono,

1067
00:57:41,860 --> 00:57:44,420
 Božić im je sve osim rođenja Isusa,

1068
00:57:44,420 --> 00:57:47,320
 i u biti svjesni smo

1069
00:57:47,320 --> 00:57:48,520
 da je Božić rođenje Isusa.

1070
00:57:48,520 --> 00:57:49,800
 Smo dušašće izgubili,

1071
00:57:49,800 --> 00:57:51,080
 bar ja to vidim.

1072
00:57:51,080 --> 00:57:52,840
 Znači, u dušašću je

1073
00:57:52,840 --> 00:57:54,580
 cijelo vrijeme neko slavlje.

1074
00:57:54,580 --> 00:57:55,480
 Ja ne kažem da,

1075
00:57:55,480 --> 00:57:56,720
 drago je i meni vidi

1076
00:57:56,720 --> 00:57:57,500
 da su ljudi veseli,

1077
00:57:57,500 --> 00:57:58,660
 volim ja biti vesela

1078
00:57:58,660 --> 00:58:00,180
 i kad se pjeva

1079
00:58:00,180 --> 00:58:02,320
 i kad je veselo i sve,

1080
00:58:02,320 --> 00:58:04,180
 ali to je vrijeme,

1081
00:58:04,180 --> 00:58:06,300
 pripreme za Božić vrijeme,

1082
00:58:06,300 --> 00:58:07,860
 gdje je mir, tišina,

1083
00:58:07,860 --> 00:58:09,100
 pripremamo srce

1084
00:58:09,100 --> 00:58:10,020
 za dolazak Isusa.

1085
00:58:10,020 --> 00:58:11,100
 Mi ne šijemo Isusa

1086
00:58:11,100 --> 00:58:12,900
 zato što smo mi okupljeni

1087
00:58:12,900 --> 00:58:14,020
 svim mogućim događenima,

1088
00:58:14,420 --> 00:58:15,960
 koji se taj događaju

1089
00:58:15,960 --> 00:58:17,560
 i nije to loše,

1090
00:58:17,560 --> 00:58:18,880
 ali trebam ostaviti

1091
00:58:18,880 --> 00:58:20,840
 bar malo mjesta za Isusa

1092
00:58:20,840 --> 00:58:23,440
 u svemu tom što se događa

1093
00:58:23,440 --> 00:58:26,000
 i nekako sam kroz ove životinice

1094
00:58:26,000 --> 00:58:26,920
 i priču u šumi

1095
00:58:26,920 --> 00:58:29,640
 baš htjela da ljudi uvide

1096
00:58:29,640 --> 00:58:31,720
 što je zapravo Došašće,

1097
00:58:31,720 --> 00:58:32,520
 a ne Božić,

1098
00:58:32,520 --> 00:58:35,100
 zato što možda je bolji naziv

1099
00:58:35,100 --> 00:58:36,520
 bio Pravi smisla Došašće,

1100
00:58:36,520 --> 00:58:37,920
 ali isli konta završava

1101
00:58:37,920 --> 00:58:39,360
 na jutro Božića,

1102
00:58:39,360 --> 00:58:40,900
 pa je zato ostao naziv

1103
00:58:40,900 --> 00:58:41,920
 Pravi smisla Božića.

1104
00:58:41,920 --> 00:58:43,120
 Toliko je prekrasna.

1105
00:58:43,300 --> 00:58:44,880
 Evo u ovoj epizodi

1106
00:58:44,880 --> 00:58:46,620
 jedna od vas će moći osvojiti

1107
00:58:46,620 --> 00:58:49,480
 Jeleninu basnu,

1108
00:58:49,480 --> 00:58:52,760
 tako da fratite nas na Instagramu

1109
00:58:52,760 --> 00:58:54,340
 da možete komentirati,

1110
00:58:54,340 --> 00:58:55,880
 lajkati,

1111
00:58:55,880 --> 00:58:58,140
 da osvojite za svoje dijete.

1112
00:58:58,140 --> 00:59:00,340
 Ovo prekrasno basnu pročitala sam je

1113
00:59:00,340 --> 00:59:02,540
 i moja djeca su oduševljena

1114
00:59:02,540 --> 00:59:04,200
 ilustracijama

1115
00:59:04,200 --> 00:59:05,460
 i evo hvala ti

1116
00:59:05,460 --> 00:59:07,760
 na toj poruci koju nosiš

1117
00:59:07,760 --> 00:59:08,580
 našoj djeci

1118
00:59:08,580 --> 00:59:11,840
 i da baš to potakneš

1119
00:59:11,840 --> 00:59:12,820
 u nama roditeljima

1120
00:59:12,820 --> 00:59:13,620
 koliko je važno

1121
00:59:13,620 --> 00:59:14,940
 stalno pričati

1122
00:59:14,940 --> 00:59:15,660
 i spominjati

1123
00:59:15,660 --> 00:59:17,540
 što je Pravi smisla

1124
00:59:17,540 --> 00:59:17,780
 Božića.

1125
00:59:17,780 --> 00:59:21,920
 Rekla si da ćeš imati

1126
00:59:21,920 --> 00:59:22,780
 promociju u Mostaru.

1127
00:59:22,780 --> 00:59:26,580
 Možeš vam evo reći

1128
00:59:26,580 --> 00:59:27,780
 neke više informacija

1129
00:59:27,780 --> 00:59:29,760
 za svoju promociju.

1130
00:59:29,840 --> 00:59:31,080
 također bit će jedna promocija

1131
00:59:31,080 --> 00:59:31,680
 u Zagrebu

1132
00:59:31,680 --> 00:59:32,860
 za sve oni koji nas prati

1133
00:59:32,860 --> 00:59:33,640
 iz Hrvatske.

1134
00:59:33,640 --> 00:59:35,840
 Pa evo možeš nam

1135
00:59:35,840 --> 00:59:36,760
 najaviti

1136
00:59:36,760 --> 00:59:37,980
 gdje te možemo prati

1137
00:59:37,980 --> 00:59:38,940
 gdje mogu ljudi

1138
00:59:38,940 --> 00:59:41,200
 kupiti tvoje priče.

1139
00:59:41,200 --> 00:59:44,260
 Sve informacije će biti

1140
00:59:44,260 --> 00:59:45,300
 na stranci

1141
00:59:45,300 --> 00:59:46,640
 mojoj pomoci

1142
00:59:46,640 --> 00:59:47,340
 mojoj nevjeri.

1143
00:59:47,340 --> 00:59:49,700
 Ja, mislim,

1144
00:59:49,700 --> 00:59:50,900
 ja ne mogu ni ljudima

1145
00:59:50,900 --> 00:59:51,780
 ni Bogu ni nikom

1146
00:59:51,780 --> 00:59:52,280
 zahvaliti.

1147
00:59:52,280 --> 00:59:53,640
 Ja svajno nisam očekivala

1148
00:59:53,640 --> 00:59:54,400
 da će ovo ovako

1149
00:59:54,400 --> 00:59:55,060
 nekako, no

1150
00:59:55,060 --> 00:59:56,100
 još niko nije.

1151
00:59:56,100 --> 00:59:57,020
 Vi ste prvi

1152
00:59:57,020 --> 00:59:58,020
 koji ste dobiti

1153
00:59:58,020 --> 00:59:58,700
 ovaj slikovici.

1154
00:59:58,800 --> 00:59:59,940
 djeca su prva vjerojatno

1155
00:59:59,940 --> 01:00:01,160
 koja su ih pročitala

1156
01:00:01,160 --> 01:00:03,020
 i stvarno je odijekla.

1157
01:00:03,020 --> 01:00:03,440
 Mislim,

1158
01:00:03,440 --> 01:00:04,880
 ajde, ono,

1159
01:00:04,880 --> 01:00:05,880
 u Mostaru kontam,

1160
01:00:05,880 --> 01:00:06,880
 ono, tamo me već ljudi

1161
01:00:06,880 --> 01:00:07,360
 znaju, ono,

1162
01:00:07,360 --> 01:00:08,460
 iskaće mi s paštete,

1163
01:00:08,460 --> 01:00:09,780
 više znaju za moj rad,

1164
01:00:09,780 --> 01:00:11,320
 ali Zagreb,

1165
01:00:11,320 --> 01:00:12,880
 ostale države

1166
01:00:12,880 --> 01:00:13,700
 po Evropi,

1167
01:00:13,700 --> 01:00:14,000
 ono,

1168
01:00:14,000 --> 01:00:15,080
 koliko znaju uopće

1169
01:00:15,080 --> 01:00:15,780
 da postoji,

1170
01:00:15,780 --> 01:00:16,620
 zato mi je bilo

1171
01:00:16,620 --> 01:00:17,440
 sve ovo čudno.

1172
01:00:17,440 --> 01:00:19,900
 Datume i lokacije,

1173
01:00:19,900 --> 01:00:20,200
 znam,

1174
01:00:20,200 --> 01:00:21,740
 Mostar je 10.11,

1175
01:00:21,740 --> 01:00:22,980
 tog u 19. sati

1176
01:00:22,980 --> 01:00:23,740
 u Kosači,

1177
01:00:23,740 --> 01:00:25,020
 to će biti baš

1178
01:00:25,020 --> 01:00:25,980
 lijepa,

1179
01:00:25,980 --> 01:00:27,420
 preskromna,

1180
01:00:27,420 --> 01:00:29,020
 po svemu će biti

1181
01:00:29,020 --> 01:00:29,580
 preskromna,

1182
01:00:29,580 --> 01:00:30,600
 jer nisam htjela da,

1183
01:00:30,600 --> 01:00:31,000
 mislim,

1184
01:00:31,000 --> 01:00:31,920
 mogla sam omgužda,

1185
01:00:31,920 --> 01:00:32,580
 to gude baš,

1186
01:00:32,580 --> 01:00:32,800
 wow,

1187
01:00:32,800 --> 01:00:33,420
 neki događaj,

1188
01:00:33,420 --> 01:00:34,640
 ali sam htjela preskromno

1189
01:00:34,640 --> 01:00:35,980
 u duhu slikovice

1190
01:00:35,980 --> 01:00:36,920
 to odraditi,

1191
01:00:37,280 --> 01:00:40,040
 tako da kratko će i trajati

1192
01:00:40,040 --> 01:00:41,040
 i bit će i zanimljivo

1193
01:00:41,040 --> 01:00:41,960
 sva što nešto

1194
01:00:41,960 --> 01:00:43,640
 smo pripremili tu,

1195
01:00:43,640 --> 01:00:45,200
 ali sve je nekako skromno,

1196
01:00:45,200 --> 01:00:46,880
 to će biti znači

1197
01:00:46,880 --> 01:00:48,720
 10.11. ponedjeljak

1198
01:00:48,720 --> 01:00:50,060
 u 19. sati

1199
01:00:50,060 --> 01:00:50,720
 u Hrvatskom domu

1200
01:00:50,720 --> 01:00:52,120
 Herceg Stjepan Kosača,

1201
01:00:52,120 --> 01:00:54,700
 zatim imamo,

1202
01:00:54,700 --> 01:00:56,220
 datume ću točno

1203
01:00:56,220 --> 01:00:57,040
 objavljivati da je

1204
01:00:57,040 --> 01:00:58,780
 21.11. Livno,

1205
01:00:58,780 --> 01:01:01,040
 u 12. mjesecu

1206
01:01:01,040 --> 01:01:02,820
 11.12. je

1207
01:01:02,820 --> 01:01:03,960
 Stolac,

1208
01:01:03,960 --> 01:01:06,280
 imamo i Ramu,

1209
01:01:06,680 --> 01:01:08,320
 imam i mnošto vrtića

1210
01:01:08,320 --> 01:01:09,620
 i škola po BiH,

